    • Method Detail

      • main

        public static void main​(java.lang.String[] args)
        Driver class Takes input from the user for the size of the hash table, the resolution type, the number of searchs and the input data file. An array is created containing the data stored within the file, the array is is then appended to the table either using linear, quadratic or chaining. The class does this by invoking the HashApp class.
        Parameters:
        args - [] table size
